<dl id="n33017c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n33" href="#n33017c">N33 (VI.B.4)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n33all.htm#n33017c"> 17(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> dhotie sahib </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: dhoti = (EB XXIV:1008) the narrow loincloth worn by Hindu men in India; sahib = a title of respect in India, especially used to designate Europeans (the word is Arabic and originally means a companion) </mm> </dd></dl>
